Colors are theme-driven. Slot N keeps its color across moves and
reorders; (name, icon) are what flow when you swap / move / rotate /
reverse / reorder. Use `ws theme NAME [--with-icons]` to change the
palette across all slots — there is no per-slot color override.
(`workspace` remains as a compat alias for muscle-memory.)

